        "gg3jo6JfgJA_text": "So what actually works?",
        "ggCisjhifSq_text": "<p>S3 certification requires specific performance standards — not a specific material. Solydia uses a Kevlar anti-puncture plate instead of steel.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Lighter, and it allows your foot to flex naturally instead of being locked rigid.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The result: 460 grams per shoe with deep heel cushioning and proper arch support built for 8+ hours on concrete.</p>",
        "ggClW72J-Oz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0673/2562/4490/files/CREA_1080X1080_-_2026-04-02T141022.667.png",
        "ggETyiUTAeB_text": "The problem isn't your feet. It's the engineering inside your boots.",
        "gga4bYgQb-e_text": "<p>Traditional Boot</p>",
        "gggbg252sNe_text": "Kevlar replaces the steel sole plate. Same S3 rating. Half the weight.",
